opinion.opinion_text: The Findings and Award of January 26, 1966 are res judicata, Wammack v. Industrial Commission, 83 Ariz. 321, 320 P.2d 950. Opinion of the Court of Appeals, 9 Ariz. App. 308, 451 P.2d 886, vacated and award of the Industrial Commission is ordered affirmed.Page 434
